#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Administration Handbook"
msgstr "Administrační příručka"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Úvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is a rich educational software suite which contains a wide range "
"of activities."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; je vysoce kvalitní vzdělávací softwarový balík, skládající se z "
"mnoha aktivit."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It offers various activities aimed at covering a variety of fields. The "
"topics include reading and typing, arithmetics, geography, sciences, and "
"other topics. It is meant to be used both at home and at school."
msgstr ""
"Nabízí různé aktivity zaměřené na pokrytí rozličných oblastí. Témata "
"zahrnují čtení a psaní, aritmetiku, zeměpis, vědu a další. Je možné jej "
"používat jak doma, tak ve škole."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The purpose of &gcompris; is to provide playful activities but always "
"educational."
msgstr ""
"Záměrem &gcompris;u je poskytnutí hravých aktivit, které jsou vždy "
"vzdělávací."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is part of &kde; project and is placed under the <ulink url="
"\"https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html\">AGPLv3 license</ulink>. All "
"the code, except the engine for analog electricity activity is under <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html\">GPLv3 license</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; je součástí projektu &kde; a je pokrytý <ulink url=\"https://www."
"gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html\">licencí AGPLv3</ulink>. Veškerý kód, vyjma "
"enginu pro aktivitu analogové elektřiny, je pokrytý <ulink url=\"https://www."
"gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html\">licencí GPLv3</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is available on the following operating systems: &GNU;/&Linux;, "
"&BSD;, &macOS;, &Windows;, Android. It requires a 3D card with support of "
"<emphasis>OpenGL 2.1</emphasis> or higher. 32 bits color depth is mandatory."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "Instalace"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The software is delivered under several forms. Follow the process according "
"to your case."
msgstr ""
"Tento software je doručován různými formami. Sledujte pokyny odpovídající "
"vaší situaci."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&GNU;/&Linux;: use the packages delivered by your &GNU;/&Linux; "
"distribution. If &gcompris; is not packaged in your &Linux; distribution, "
"please contact them to ask for the inclusion of &gcompris;."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&Windows;: delivered under a classic installer for &Windows; or via the "
"Microsoft Store."
msgstr ""
"&Windows;: doručení pomocí klasického instalátoru pro &Windows; nebo skrze "
"obchod Microsoft Store."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "&macOS;: delivered under a classic installer."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Android: distributed by the F-Droid store or Google Play Store. APK file is "
"also available."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "The User Interface"
msgstr "Uživatelské rozhraní"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The interface is designed for easy use by small children. &gcompris; is "
"controlled with a mouse. Keyboard navigation is also available on most of "
"the activities."
msgstr ""
"Rozhraní je navrženo pro snadně použití malými dětmi. &gcompris; je  "
"ovládaný myší. Také je ve většině aktivit dostupná navigace pomocí  "
"klávesnice."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main window"
msgstr "Hlavní okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start the program, &gcompris; shows a graphical interface which "
"presents the list of activities with a control bar at the bottom."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here’s a screenshot of &gcompris; main window"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "&gcompris; Main Window"
msgstr "Hlavní okno &gcompris;u"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each icon represents an activity. Around each one, you can find small icons "
"which give additional information about the activity. A simple click on the "
"icon will lead you to an activity or a menu of activities. There are 8 "
"sections (categories) of activities, which are placed on the top or on the "
"left (only if your orientation is portrait). For example, there is section "
"“Board Games”, which includes board games, like Chess, Tic-Tac-Toe or Align "
"Four."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some categories have subcategories to better filter the activities. For math "
"activities, we have three subcategories: numeration, arithmetic and measures."
msgstr ""
"Některé z kategorií mají podkategorie pro lepší filtrování aktivit. Pro "
"matematické  aktivity tu máme 3 podkategorie: Číslování, výpočty a míry."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "The stars indicate the age group for which each game is designed:"
msgstr ""
"Počet hvězd u aktivity říká pro jakou věkovou skupinu je aktivita určena:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "1, 2 or 3 yellow stars — for 2 to 6 years old."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "1, 2 or 3 red stars — greater than 6 years old."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the screen there is a control bar for &gcompris;. The "
"possible icons are (the icons are only displayed if they are available in "
"the activity):"
msgstr ""
"Na spodní straně obrazovky je ovládací lišta &gcompris;u. Zobrazují se  zde "
"(pokud jsou pro danou aktivitu dostupné) následující ikony:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Home — Leaves the current activity, returns to the previous menu."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"“OK” — Validate, confirm your answer. Some activities do not detect "
"automatically whether or not the child has completed the task. In this case, "
"you have to click on this icon. You can also use the &Enter; key on your "
"keyboard."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Light — Display a hint for the activity. We can help the children on some "
"activities to guide them to find the answers."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Arrows — The present level is displayed. Click on one of the arrows to "
"select another level. Generally, the activities offer several levels whose "
"numbers depend on the activity. In &gcompris;, it is possible to go to the "
"next level without having completed the current level."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lips — Ask &gcompris; to repeat the question."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Question mark — Display the help dialog box. Sometimes, an activity can be "
"too complex to be described easily in the description area. In this case, "
"this function gives access to additional information."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tool box — Configuration menu. The configuration is saved in the user "
"repository (folder) under the name <filename>.config/gcompris/gcompris-qt."
"conf</filename>. This is a text file which can be edited manually."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"List item — Display the activity settings menu. There are two possible tabs "
"here. First one, “Dataset”, allows to choose the levels of the activities "
"depending on several objectives and the second one, “Options”, allows to "
"update the configuration of the activity if available."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Capital “G” — Information box on &gcompris;, presents the main contributors "
"and the version of the software."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Power — Quit &gcompris;. You can also use the shortcut on your keyboard "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kiosk Mode"
msgstr "Režim kiosku"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you use &gcompris; with small children or on a self-service kiosk, you "
"can disable a certain number of options:"
msgstr ""
"Pokud &gcompris; používají malé děti nebo je spuštěný na samoobslužném  "
"kiosku, můžete v něm zakázat určitý počet možností:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris --enable-kioskmode</command></userinput>: "
"disable the <guiicon>Quit</guiicon> and <guiicon>Configuration</guiicon> "
"buttons."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris --disable-kioskmode</command></userinput>: "
"enable the <guiicon>Quit</guiicon> and <guiicon>Configuration</guiicon> "
"buttons."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris -f</command></userinput>: run &gcompris; in "
"fullscreen mode"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>gcompris -C</command></userinput>: disable the cursor "
"(touch screen mode)"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "These options can of course be combined."
msgstr "Tyto volby mohou být samozřejmě kombinovány."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyboard Shortcuts"
msgstr "Klávesové zkratky"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcut"
msgstr "Zkratka"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Action"
msgstr "Akce"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Esc; or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo>"
msgstr ""
"&Esc; nebo <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quit the current activity or dialog then return to the main menu."
msgstr "Ukončit současnou aktivitu nebo dialog pro návrat do hlavní nabídky."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quit &gcompris; without further notice."
msgstr "Ukončit &gcompris; bez dalšího upozornění."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle fullscreen mode."
msgstr "Přepnout režim celé obrazovky."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle sound mute."
msgstr "Přepnout ztlumení zvuku."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display or hide the control bar."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Notes on Internationalization"
msgstr "Poznámky o internacionalizaci"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is internationalized and is available in more than 35 languages. "
"If you want to check if your language is available, you can start &gcompris; "
"and select your language in the option of configuration."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; je internacionalizovaný a dostupný ve více než 35 jazycích. "
"Pokud  chceš zjistit, zda je tvůj jazyk dostupný, můžeš spustit &gcompris; a "
"vybrat  tvůj jazyk ve volbách konfigurace."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Be careful, some languages need specific fonts to be displayed correctly."
msgstr ""
"Pozor, některé jazyky vyžadují pro své správné zobrazení specifické fonty."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your language is not supported, you can contribute to the software and "
"add the translation of your language. If you are interested, you can contact "
"the <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/teams\">translation team</ulink> of "
"the &kde; project for your language. You can check the level of translation "
"for your language on the <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/\">&kde; "
"translation web site</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Pokud tvůj jazyk není podporován, můžeš přispět k tomuto softwaru a přidat  "
"překlad svého jazyka. Pokud tě to zaujalo, můžeš kontaktovat <ulink  url="
"\"https://l10n.kde.org/teams\">překladatelský tým</ulink> tvého jazyka  v "
"projektu &kde;. Úroveň překladu tvého jazyka můžeš zkontrolovat na  <ulink "
"url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/\">překladatelské stránce &kde;</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid "Language learning"
msgstr "Výuka jazyka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use &gcompris; in a foreign language that you are learning. Select a "
"foreign language in the configuration menu. Do not forget to download the "
"optional audio modules for this language."
msgstr ""
"Pokud se učíš cizí jazyk, můžeš &gcompris; používat v daném jazyce. Cizí "
"jazyk si můžeš vybrat v nabídce konfigurace. Nezapomeň si pro tento jazyk "
"stáhnout  volitelné audio moduly."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Customizing activities"
msgstr "Úprava aktivit"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can customize some activities using the configuration button in them. "
"For example, you can set the locale in some text activities (like "
"wordsgame), or make it show real car images instead of filled rectangles "
"(traffic)."
msgstr ""
"Některé aktivity můžeš upravovat za použití jejich tlačítka konfigurace. "
"Například  můžeš nastavit místní jazyk v některých aktivitách s textem (jako "
"je hra se slovy)  nebo můžeš si zobrazit obrázky skutečných aut namísto "
"vyplněných obdélníků  (hra s posouváním bloků)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For multiple activities, you can choose several datasets in the "
"configuration. Each one has a specific objective which is described."
msgstr ""
"Pro několik aktivit si můžeš v konfiguraci vybrat různé datové sady. Každá "
"má nějaké určité cíle, které jsou popsány."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Dataset of activity “Count the items”</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Dataset of activity “Count the items”</phrase>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can choose the options for this activity."
msgstr "Pro tuto aktivitu můžeš nastavit volby."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Select mode of activity “Count the items”</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Select mode of activity “Count the items”</phrase>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Console Parameters"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Running &gcompris; from a command console with the “--help” option will "
"display all the parameters it accepts:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid "-f, --fullscreen"
msgstr "-f, --fullscreen"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; in fullscreen mode."
msgstr "Spustit &gcompris; v režimu celé obrazovky."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid "-w, --window"
msgstr "-w, --window"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; in window mode."
msgstr "Spustit &gcompris; v režimu okna."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "-s, --sound"
msgstr "-s, --sound"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; with sound enabled."
msgstr "Spustit &gcompris; se zapnutým zvukem."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "-m, --mute"
msgstr "-m, --mute"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; without sound."
msgstr "Spustit &gcompris; bez zvuku."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "-c, --cursor"
msgstr "-c, --cursor"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; with the default system cursor."
msgstr "Spustit &gcompris; s výchozím systémovým kurzorem."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "-C, --nocursor"
msgstr "-C, --nocursor"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run &gcompris; without cursor (touch screen mode)."
msgstr "Spustit &gcompris; bez kurzoru (režim dotykové obrazovky)."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "-v, --version"
msgstr "-v, --version"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid "Print the version of &gcompris;."
msgstr "Vytisknout verzi &gcompris;u."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "-l, --list-activities"
msgstr "-l, --list-activities"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Outputs all the available activities on the standard output."
msgstr "Vypíše všechny dostupné aktivity na standardní výstup."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid "--launch activity"
msgstr "--launch aktivita"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify the activity when starting &gcompris;."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "--start-level level"
msgstr "--start-level úroveň"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Specify the level on which to start the activity specified by “--launch” "
"option when starting &gcompris;. Ignored if no “--launch” option, or if "
"level specified is invalid."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid "--difficulty {value|min-max}"
msgstr "--difficulty {hodnota|minimum-maximum}"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For the session, force &gcompris; activities difficulty to be either at "
"value or between min and max values. The values must be between 1 and 6, and "
"if the format is min-max, the min value must be lower than the max value. If "
"it is not the case &gcompris; will not start."
